        div.container-fluid.turn_scree_captures_section
            div.row
                div.turn_scree_captures
                    h5 Turn Screen Captures into Stylish Masterpieces.
                    p Start Creating. Start Impressing.
                    a.btn.btn-primary.ScreenGenius_todaybtn(href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/screengenius-screenshot-s/eclnikmacpcandpbfjkjgnoicmlpkkdj") Get Chrome Extension
                        img(src="images/get-ext-arrow.png")
                div.turn_scree_captures_feature
                    span.camraIcon
                        img(src="images/home/camra.png")
                        p Dab to fab Snaps!
                    span.otherScreen
                        img(src="images/home/recording.png")
                        p Record. Share. Wow!
                    span.otherScreen
                        img(src="images/home/download.png")
                        p Seamless Cloud Peace
                    span.otherScreen
                        img(src="images/home/synk.png")
                        p Snap. Sync. Access
        div.container#screenshot-tab
            div.row
                div.section_title
                    h1 Screenshot Smarter. Not Harder.
                    p Spark inspiration, share ideas, & ignite conversations
                div.col-lg-6.d-flex.flex-column.justify-content-center.conversations-mid.screenshots
                    img(src="images/home/activatity.png")
                
                div.col-lg-6.conversations-mid
                    span.screenshot_smarter
                        img(src="images/home/cam-camra.png")
                        h5 Capture screen like a boss!
                        p Snap full screen area, visible area or select as you wish
                    span.screenshot_smarter
                        img(src="images/home/edit_icon.png")
                        h5 Edit & Annotate your heart's content
                        p Crop it, add text, highlights, blur & other effects with ease.
                    span.screenshot_smarter
                        img(src="images/home/share.png")
                        h5 Be ready to share a flick
                        p Upload to cloud, share via link or by email
                    span.screenshot_smarter
                        img(src="images/home/menu.png")
                        h5 All media roads lead to dashboard!
                        p View, access, manage screenshots through dashboard
        div.container-fluid.screen_recording_game
            div.container#screen-recording-tab
                div.row
                    div.section_title
                        h1 Take your Screen Recording game up a notch!
                        p Captivate, educate or entertain. Make people engage with your content like never before
                    div.col-lg-6.conversations-mid
                        span.take_your_screen
                            img(src="images/home/vid-camra.png")
                            h5 Capture screen like a boss!
                            p Snap full screen area, visible area or select as you wish
                        span.take_your_screen
                            img(src="images/home/edit_icon.png")
                            h5 Edit & Annotate your heart's content
                            p Crop it, add text, highlights, blur & other effects with ease.
                        span.take_your_screen
                            img(src="images/home/share.png")
                            h5 Be ready to share a flick
                            p Upload to cloud, share via link or by email
                        span.take_your_screen
                            img(src="images/home/menu.png")
                            h5 All media roads lead to dashboard!
                            p View, access, manage screenshots through dashboard
                    div.col-lg-6.d-flex.flex-column.justify-content-center.conversations-mid.screenshots
                        img(src="images/home/activatity2.png")      
        div.container-fluid.features_in_beta
            div.container#pricing-plans-tab
                div.row
                    div.section_title
                        h1 Drumroll please! It's our beta launch
                        p Ready to make it to the next level? Soon will be launching our paid plans, perfect for those looking to scale their use
                    div.features_in_beta_plan
                        span.features_in_beta_plan_span
                            h5 Features in Beta
                            p 3 free announcements / Month
                            ul
                                li
                                    img(src="images/home/bxs-check-circle.png") 
                                    span Unlimited Local Captures & Recording
                                li
                                    img(src="images/home/bxs-check-circle.png") 
                                    span 15 Screen Recordings on Cloud
                                li
                                    img(src="images/home/bxs-check-circle.png") 
                                    span 30 Screenshots on Cloud
                                li
                                    img(src="images/home/bxs-check-circle.png") 
                                    span Editors for both Images and Videos
                                li
                                    img(src="images/home/bxs-check-circle.png") 
                                    span Share them infinitely
                            a.btn.btn-primary.chrome-thisbtn(href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/screengenius-screenshot-s/eclnikmacpcandpbfjkjgnoicmlpkkdj") Get Chrome Extension
        div.container-fluid.frequently_asked_questions
            div.container#frequently-asked-questions
                div.row
                    div.section_title
                        h1 Frequently Asked Questions
                    div.col-lg-6
                        span
                            h6 Is ScreenGenius free? Any number limit on the screenshots & recordings I do?
                            p Yes, it's absolutely free as of now, so take advantage of that as much as you can.
                        span
                            h6 How can I upgrade to the premium version?
                            p Premium version is on the card. As this is a beta launch, we'll soon notify you once upgrade is available.
                        span
                            h6 Till when my generated share links will be valid?
                            p All your screenshots & screen recordings links are here to stay, as long as you want to keep them in public.
                    div.col-lg-6
                        span
                            h6 Can I be worry-free that my data is safe with ScreenGenius?
                            p No doubt for that. Your data safety & security is our top priority. You can relax, your information is in safe hands.
                        span
                            h6 What if I got a special feature request?
                            p We're all ears for that. Though we can't promise the timelines but we pay attention to all ideas. Please submit your request in feedback section.
                        span
                            h6 Can I access ScreenGenius from all of my devices?
                            p A big yes to that. Access from any device without any restrictions.
        div.container.ScreenGenius_today
            div.row
                span
                    h4 Try ScreenGenius today!
                    a.btn.btn-primary.ScreenGenius_todaybtn(href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/screengenius-screenshot-s/eclnikmacpcandpbfjkjgnoicmlpkkdj") Get Chrome Extension
                        img(src="images/get-ext-arrow.png")
        div.footer
            div.container
                div.row
                    div.col-lg-4
                        span
                            img(src="images/home/footer-logo.png").sitetitle
                            p 
                                span Screenshots & Screen recordings 
                                span with a dash of your unique personality.
                    div.col-lg-4
                        span
                            ul
                                li 
                                    a(href="#") About us
                                li 
                                    a(href="#") Feedback
                                li 
                                    a(href="#") Privacy
                    div.col-lg-4
                        span
                            h5 Contact us
                            p Please contact us at the given email address. We will get back to you within 24 hours.
                            p 
                                a(mailto="support@screengenius.io") support@screengenius.io
